      "Replace 'values' array with your data",
      "Change field names in scales, axes, and marks to match your data",
      "Update axes titles to include your units",
      "Adjust x/y scale domains and zero:false as needed for your data range",
      "Modify title and description for your context"
    ],
    "dataFormat": "Array of objects with 'x' (quantitative), 'y' (quantitative), 'category' (nominal for color), and 'label' (nominal identifier) fields."
  },
  "$schema": "https://vega.github.io/schema/vega/v6.json",
